<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc7bbd58-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s3274"><num value="3274">§ 3274.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the purposes of this chapter, such sums to remain available until expended.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbc7bbd59-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/560/s4">Pub. L. 89–560, § 4</ref>, <date date="1966-09-07">Sept. 7, 1966</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/80/706">80 Stat. 706</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
